This paper is about natural language understanding and learning semantic representations, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses learning policies and optimization, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of QA-SRL, which is a task related to natural language processing and computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the paper discusses data efficiency, which is a topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
